<p>The platform is owned and maintained by the same company as the Bitfinex exchange, but offers <a href="/dex-trading/">non-custodial crypto trading</a>.</p>

<p>On DeversiFi, you trade crypto directly from your <a href="/altcoin-wallets/">hardware or software cryptocurrency wallet</a> without signup.</p>

